User Enumeration

Windows
- net user

Linux
- cat /etc/passwd
- who
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Process Enumeration

Windows
- tasklist /v

Linux
- ps -elf
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Service Enumeration

Windows
- tasklist /svc

Linux
- chkconfig              
- systemctl --type=service
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Network Connection Enumeration

Windows
- ipconfig /all

Linux
- ifconfig -a
- ip a
